    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    display: flex;<section class="jobs-section">
  <h2>Jobs & Internship Opportunities</h2>
  <p>Explore available job and internship opportunities in the field of environmental sustainability, plastic management, and more. Apply now and contribute to the change!</p>

