<section>
  <h2>Suggested Solutions</h2>
  <div class="solution">
    <ul>
      <li>Deploy more waste bins in high-traffic areas.</li>
      <li>Partner with Agroplast to recycle collected plastics.</li>
      <li>Community awareness campaigns on waste sorting.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Prevention Strategies</h2>
  <p>Encourage source separation at household level. Create a plastic-for-points rewards system to boost community participation.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Proposed Projects</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Plastic-to-Bricks Innovation:</strong> Partner with local companies like Agroplast to turn waste into building materials.</li>
